SQL_STMT_U.val: select CLNT101_ADMNO, CLNT102_CLNTNO from :1/CLNT join :1/ADMN on ADMN_NO = CLNT101_ADMNO and ADMN_VORTEXREPORTING = 'Y' exception join :1/VT01 on VT01_DATE = ':2' and VT01_ADMNO = CLNT101_ADMNO and VT01_CLNTNO = CLNT102_CLNTNO where not(CLNT102_CLNTNO in (99998, 999999)) and (CLNT804_TYPEOFINVESTMENT = 10 or CLNT804_TYPEOFINVESTMENT = 14) :3 for fetch only
select count(*) from :1/VT01 where year(VT01_DATE) = :2 and VT01_CLNTNO>0 for fetch only

select VT01_ADMNO, VT01_CLNTNO, max(VT01_DATE), min(VT01_LOCALCUSTOMERID) from :1/VT01 where year(VT01_DATE) = :2 and VT01_CLNTNO>0 :3 group by VT01_ADMNO, VT01_CLNTNO order by VT01_ADMNO, VT01_CLNTNO for fetch only

Text.val: calc for v.sum(LGCC_AMOUNTH)_11
calc for v.sum(LGCC_AMOUNTH)_13
calc for v.sum(LGCC_AMOUNTH)_15
calc for v.sum(LGCC_AMOUNTH)_17
-- CMON_AVGINVESTMENT (19), CMON_TOTAPAYCR (33)
calc v.LEGALINV
v.sum (LGCC_AMOUNTH)_29

SQL_STMT_U.val: select cast (sum (LGCC_AMOUNTH) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/LGCC, :1/LDGR where LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO = :2 and LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO = :3 and LDGR_ADMNO = LGCC_LGCD_ADMNO and LDGR_NO = LGCC_LDGR_NO and LDGR_INCOMETYPE = :4 and :5 for fetch only

select cast (sum (CMON_CURRBALINVESTMENT) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/CMON where CMON_CURRENCY = ':4' and :5 and exists(select * from :1/VT01 where VT01_LEGAL_ADMNO = :2 and VT01_LEGAL_CLNTNO = :3 and CMON_ADMNO = VT01_ADMNO and CMON_CLNTNO = VT01_CLNTNO ) for fetch only
select cast (sum (LGCC_AMOUNTH) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/LGCC where LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO = :2 and LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO = :3 and LGCC_LDGR_NO in (44410, 44411, 44416, 44417) and :4 for fetch only

select cast (sum (CDHI_AMOUNTHELL) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/CDHI a join :1/CDEP on CDEP_ADMNO = a.CDHI_ADMNO and CDEP_CLNTNO = a.CDHI_CLNTNO and CDEP_DEPNO = a.CDHI_DEPNO and CDEP_ADMNO = :3 and CDEP_CLNTNO = :4 :5 where a.CDHI_DATE <= ':2' and a.CDHI_LINENO = (select max(b.CDHI_LINENO) from :1/CDHI b where b.CDHI_ADMNO= a.CDHI_ADMNO and b.CDHI_CLNTNO = a.CDHI_CLNTNO and b.CDHI_DEPNO = a.CDHI_DEPNO and b.CDHI_DATE <= ':2') for fetch only

select cast (sum (CMON_AVGINVESTMENT) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum (CMON_TOTAPAYCR) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/CMON where CMON_ADMNO = :2 and CMON_CLNTNO = :3 and CMON_CURRENCY = ':4' and CMON_YEAR = :5 and CMON_MONTH <= :6 for fetch only
